，後來相約女童在天水圍區見面，期間涉嫌非禮兩名女童。其後他在6月6日，涉嫌「非禮」及「向年齡在16歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為」被拘捕，獲准保釋候查，須於七月上旬向警方報到，案件由新界北總區重案組跟進。男警隨後已被警方停職，豈知停職期間再涉嫌犯下強姦案。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1760092/org/a6371f5fdf7d9947bd11ae27abf4f37a.jpg/LdqCAsd5me42-Al2LPXUkzbIx1eQ93ORvO5cSrzuXEo?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1760092%2Forg%2Fa6371f5fdf7d9947bd11ae27abf4f37a.jpg%2FLdqCAsd5me42-Al2LPXUkzbIx1eQ93ORvO5cSrzuXEo%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=8db7b796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉案男警在停職期間，與一名14歲女童到蘭桂坊消遣，其後在沙田公屋梯間強姦該名女童。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"大家要煲大！"},{"pid":"a421406978a3220f609a03911896fa8e1b21103c","tid":1921884,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e90d749499cd91260851ec05f9aa4117332d4ba1","tid":1921884,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96096d9d5083fab227a6a7ac552f1f6d94043e21","tid":1921884,"uid":19552,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"警隊根本係爛仔竇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"一堆柴狼"},{"pid":"342dd982e10d3625e9201790e7db89c59923f570","tid":1921884,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca7b3e5167cdd14ef05cbf8ec354f4c3ba477ec1","tid":1921884,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:21:50.000Z","msg":"閹咗隻狗公去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbcc218222c82226bccc1ca0e81fe239797479f","tid":1921884,"uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f0e884b88e509fba6bc6876661629e5d940867","tid":1921884,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"